		{"id":"ff8a9943ca2c1a9b","type":"text","text":"([Wenger 等, 2018, p. 197](zotero://select/library/items/DMSVNNUT)) ([pdf](zotero://open-pdf/library/items/VH36Z6AQ?page=3&annotation=VFUXHE53)) TTFIELDS 的计算模型","x":-880,"y":115,"width":250,"height":125},
		{"id":"f7ff902b1a66b0fb","type":"text","text":"([Wenger 等, 2018, p. 197](zotero://select/library/items/DMSVNNUT)) ([pdf](zotero://open-pdf/library/items/VH36Z6AQ?page=3&annotation=6XSXFW6L)) EF 分布都是通过应用体积导体模型 [1] 来以适当的边界条件 （BC） 对麦克斯韦电动力学方程的导数进行数值求解来近似的","x":-880,"y":320,"width":250,"height":207},
