		{"id":"5cbb5e2551a30fff","type":"file","file":"LiteratureNotes/a review on tumor-treating fields (ttfields)clinical implications inferred from computational modeling肿瘤治疗电场 （ttfields） 综述从计算建模推断的临床意义附件/A Review on Tumor-Treating Fields (TTFields)Clinical Implications Inferred From Computational Modeling肿瘤治疗电场 （TTFields） 综述从计算建模推断的临床意义-pasted image 20250425190332.png","x":960,"y":1156,"width":241,"height":225},
		{"id":"16f29521908ffa91","type":"text","text":"([Wenger 等, 2018, p. 202](zotero://select/library/items/DMSVNNUT)) ([pdf](zotero://open-pdf/library/items/VH36Z6AQ?page=8&annotation=A25JYMNH)) 🔤基于模拟的研究表明，TTFields 在大脑内的分布是异质的 [72]、[73]、[79]、[100]，并受到复杂组织界面的影响，尤其是不同组织介电特性的差异。🔤","x":179,"y":1781,"width":250,"height":238},
		{"id":"81eca92a69bc8353","type":"text","text":"影响因素","x":-5,"y":2080,"width":128,"height":60},
		{"id":"851749bd51f00774","type":"text","text":"([Wenger 等, 2018, p. 202](zotero://select/library/items/DMSVNNUT)) ([pdf](zotero://open-pdf/library/items/VH36Z6AQ?page=8&annotation=BWMVNZF4)) 🔤最高的场强出现在靠近有源换能器阵列的头皮和颅骨中。🔤","x":424,"y":1951,"width":208,"height":148},
		{"id":"44701581ded8d330","type":"text","text":" ([Wenger 等, 2018, p. 202](zotero://select/library/items/DMSVNNUT)) ([pdf](zotero://open-pdf/library/items/VH36Z6AQ?page=8&annotation=3FU9884U)) 🔤在肿瘤内，在坏死核心中发现低场值，而在肿瘤和瘤周边界区发现分布不均匀的较高值🔤","x":179,"y":2051,"width":250,"height":178},
		{"id":"8390e5b5fea66fad","type":"text","text":"[Wenger 等, 2018, p. 203](zotero://select/library/items/DMSVNNUT)) ([pdf](zotero://open-pdf/library/items/VH36Z6AQ?page=9&annotation=FL6AUZZQ)) 🔤这是因为对于 TTFields 设置，电流主要是电阻性的，而不是电容性的，即 σ ωε0εr [102]。此外，这一结果验证了通过忽略介电常数来考虑静态问题的方法，就像在使用 SimNibs 进行的患者研究中所做的那样。🔤","x":429,"y":2172,"width":337,"height":208},
		{"id":"b1c3af296650ee6b","type":"text","text":"[Wenger 等, 2018, p. 203](zotero://select/library/items/DMSVNNUT)) ([pdf](zotero://open-pdf/library/items/VH36Z6AQ?page=9&annotation=5TVUT3GD)) 🔤计算结果表明，肿瘤形状和大小（高达 26.6 cm3 的总体积）对肿瘤中的平均 EF 强度没有明显影响，这主要是由于单个阵列的大尺寸","x":174,"y":2276,"width":250,"height":208},
		{"id":"ef87f315ab872e0c","type":"text","text":"([Wenger 等, 2018, p. 204](zotero://select/library/items/DMSVNNUT)) ([pdf](zotero://open-pdf/library/items/VH36Z6AQ?page=10&annotation=Y4VILR4C)) 🔤这些研究表明，单个头部的形状和大小以及组织隔室的几何形状和厚度 [100] 在很大程度上影响了头部内的 TTFields 分布。🔤","x":429,"y":2395,"width":307,"height":178},
		{"id":"7efd5259f4198aa9","type":"text","text":"结论：\n([Wenger 等, 2018, p. 205](zotero://select/library/items/DMSVNNUT)) ([pdf](zotero://open-pdf/library/items/VH36Z6AQ?page=11&annotation=3JL27ZHX)) 🔤总之，TTFields 是另一种应用，其中计算建模是进一步开发和提高疗效不可或缺的一部分。🔤","x":1340,"y":366,"width":250,"height":208},
		{"id":"4c5e4b5b6de454ea","type":"text","text":"([Wenger 等, 2018, p. 197](zotero://select/library/items/DMSVNNUT)) ([pdf](zotero://open-pdf/library/items/VH36Z6AQ?page=3&annotation=76CNFH2I)) 🔤1） 材料和方法：🔤","x":-93,"y":-163,"width":213,"height":87},
		{"id":"15d6bd2d7a1c7af2","type":"text","text":" ([Wenger 等, 2018, p. 197](zotero://select/library/items/DMSVNNUT)) ([pdf](zotero://open-pdf/library/items/VH36Z6AQ?page=3&annotation=4QAH85JY)) 模拟 TTFields 应用于单细胞的研究[20]、[44]-[46]假定球形细胞在分裂期的默认半径为 10 微米。在端期和细胞分裂过程中，椭圆形姐妹细胞的默认主要半径为 10 μm，次要半径为 7 μm。随着分裂的进行，姊妹细胞之间的切口平面长度（沟槽长度）逐渐减小，从而模拟了端期的三个不同阶段（见图 1 底图中的红线）。","x":200,"y":-540,"width":250,"height":93},
		{"id":"c60cc871c09fb915","type":"text","text":"([Wenger 等, 2018, p. 197](zotero://select/library/items/DMSVNNUT)) ([pdf](zotero://open-pdf/library/items/VH36Z6AQ?page=3&annotation=66FZJZ9W)) 这些模型由三个结构域组成：细胞外空间、胞质溶胶和膜，它们的介电特性不同。","x":240,"y":-420,"width":240,"height":148},
		{"id":"685434152168acaa","type":"text","text":"([Wenger 等, 2018, p. 198](zotero://select/library/items/DMSVNNUT)) ([pdf](zotero://open-pdf/library/items/VH36Z6AQ?page=4&annotation=TB23L6UQ)) 为了应用均匀的 EF，选择两个相对侧面的 BC 作为电压类型的端子，其他的都是电绝缘的，代表了理想的平行板电极设置。","x":200,"y":-241,"width":250,"height":207},
